column2: This kit is guaranteed to remove upgrades from any sort of armor, weapon, or trinket and +50%% chance for rare materials of better quality. (25 charges)

<c=@flavor>Lift up thy weapons. For you are my soldiers, and must you be steadfast, strong, and brave of heart. They who neither hesitate nor stumble shall be rewarded." -Scriptures of Balthazar, 48 BE</c>"
